- Give me a call.

500
00:27:00.368 --> 00:27:01.494
That would be so awesome.

501
00:27:01.578 --> 00:27:02.888
- Thank you so much.
- You bet.

502
00:27:02.912 --> 00:27:04.623
So. the Lexus.

503
00:27:04.706 --> 00:27:05.999
