when the truth be told.

532
00:28:05.058 --> 00:28:06.827
the current situation
is probably a whole nother thing.

533
00:28:06.851 --> 00:28:08.411
- Oh...
- Look. I work at a bureaucracy.

534
00:28:08.436 --> 00:28:10.122
I'm telling you.
you're not gonna get anywhere

535
00:28:10.146 --> 00:28:11.940
chewing out some low-level yes-man.

536
00:28:12.023 --> 00:28:13.817
