- Yeah.

550
00:28:37.549 --> 00:28:39.968
"The current situation is probably
a whole nother thing."

551
00:28:40.051 --> 00:28:41.720
Sweet sweating Jesus. Kendra.

552
00:28:41.803 --> 00:28:43.364
