really that delicate?

598
00:30:41.840 --> 00:30:44.342
Of course not. Kenny. Come on.

599
00:30:44.843 --> 00:30:46.483
It's just a hell of a fun button to push.

600
00:30:46.511 --> 00:30:49.305
His name is fine. all right?

601
