629
00:32:20.146 --> 00:32:21.397
Please don't go there.

630
00:32:21.481 --> 00:32:23.417
We haven't really
seen each other since... you know.

631
00:32:23.441 --> 00:32:25.001
- Oh. I know.
- Oh. can't I just notice?

632
00:32:25.068 --> 00:32:26.152
